    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has a severe oil leak and struggles to idle, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is strictly a mechanic's special or a parts car for someone willing to invest the necessary time and resources into a full restoration.",
