    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolutely pristine condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like a total dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless and ready to hit the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
