    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. The S54 3.2L power plant remains in peak mechanical health, exhibiting precise VANOS timing and optimal compression across all six cylinders. Shifting is handled by a robust six-speed manual gearbox with crisp synchros, delivering torque through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally pristine, with a reinforced rear subframe and an OEM suspension geometry that retains its original dampening characteristics and torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless clear coat and an impeccable Nappa leather interior, this vehicle is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromised performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Clean title. Inspection ready.",
