    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it rolled off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirls, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather still retains its factory scent, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records to prove its pedigree. Always garaged under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title, ready for its next caretaker.",
