      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), a definitive driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving 3.6L M96/03 flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This unit features the desirable 6-speed manual G96 transaxle, providing precise shift throws and a direct mechanical connection. The vehicle is mechanically superlative; the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the Rear Main Seal (RMS) is bone dry. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, supported by original Bilstein dampers and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers. With flawless paint depth and documented service history, this is an investment-grade 996 for the discerning collector.",
